Package: proteomicAge
Type: Package
Title: Proteomic Aging Clocks
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xiaohan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xiaohan@clawbio.org")
  )
Description: Compute biological age from plasma proteomic data using
    published proteomic aging clocks. Currently implements the Tanaka
    et al. (2018) 76-protein elastic net clock trained on SOMAscan
    1.3K data. Additional clocks (Lehallier 2019, Lehallier 2020,
    Sathyan 2020) will be added in future releases. All computation
    is local — proteomic data never leaves the machine.
